<h1>Privacy Policy</h1>

<p>
This Privacy Policy describes how this mobile application ("the App") handles user information.
By using the App, you agree to the terms described in this policy.
</p>

<h2>Information Collection and Use</h2>

<p>
The App itself does not collect, store, or require any personal information such as name, email address,
phone number, or account details.
</p>

<p>
The App does not require user registration or login.
</p>

<h2>Advertising</h2>

<p>
The App displays banner advertisements provided by <b>Google AdMob</b>.
</p>

<p>
Google AdMob may automatically collect certain information, including but not limited to:
</p>

<ul>
  <li>Device information</li>
  <li>Advertising ID</li>
  <li>IP address</li>
  <li>Approximate location</li>
</ul>

<p>
This information is used for ad personalisation, ad measurement, analytics, and improving advertising services.
The App developer does not have direct access to this data.
</p>

<p>
For more information about how Google uses data, please refer to:
<br>
https://policies.google.com/privacy
</p>

<h2>Cookies</h2>

<p>
The App itself does not use cookies.
However, Google AdMob may use cookies or similar technologies as part of its advertising services.
</p>

<h2>Third-Party Services</h2>

<p>
The App uses third-party services that may collect information used to identify you.
</p>

<ul>
  <li>Google Play Services</li>
  <li>Google AdMob</li>
</ul>

<h2>Childrenâ€™s Privacy</h2>

<p>
The App is not directed to children under the age of 13.
The App does not knowingly collect personal information from children.
</p>

<p>
If you are a parent or guardian and you are aware that your child has provided personal information
through third-party services, please contact the relevant service provider.
</p>

<h2>Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>

<p>
This Privacy Policy may be updated from time to time.
